epel：
参考：https://support.rackspace.com/how-to/install-epel-and-additional-repositories-on-centos-and-red-hat/
以及：http://www.tecmint.com/how-to-enable-epel-repository-for-rhel-centos-6-5/

按照第一个链接，输入：
sudo yum install epel-release
成功！

按照第二个链接，输入：
yum repolist
报告：
epel/x86_64 Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux 7 - x86_64    9,697

Coprs//librehat：
参考：https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/librehat/
sudo wget https://copr.fedorainfracloud.org/coprs/librehat/shadowsocks/repo/epel-7/librehat-shadowsocks-epel-7.repo -O /etc/yum.repos.d/
接着：
yum install shadowsocks-libev





